'''“抵制、撤资、制裁”'''（{{lang-en|Boycott, Divestment and Sanctions Movement}}，简称“'''BDS运动'''”）是自2005年7月9日起，由[[英國|英國]]社會運動組織一项全球性的运动<ref name="Svirsky2011">{{cite book|author=Marcelo Svirsky|title=Arab-Jewish activism in Israel-Palestine|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=iQj5GhqfMloC&pg=PA123|accessdate=3 June 2013|date=28 October 2011|publisher=Ashgate Publishing, Ltd.|isbn=978-1-4094-2229-7|page=121|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810133207/http://books.google.com/books?id=iQj5GhqfMloC&pg=PA123|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目的是向[[以色列|以色列]]施压，呼吁以色列政府停止占领[[巴勒斯坦国|巴勒斯坦国]]的领土，尊重[[阿拉伯裔以色列人|阿拉伯裔以色列人]]的平等权益，並尊重居於海外的巴勒斯坦难民的回归权。<ref name="Svirsky2011"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Introducing the BDS Movement|url=http://www.bdsmovement.net/bdsintro|publisher=Palestinian BDS National Committee|accessdate=14 January 2015|quote="The call urges various forms of boycott against Israel until it meets its obligations under international law by: Ending its occupation and colonization of all Arab lands occupied in June 1967 and dismantling the Wall; Recognizing the fundamental rights of the Arab-Palestinian citizens of Israel to full equality; and Respecting, protecting and promoting the rights of Palestinian refugees to return to their homes and properties as stipulated in UN Resolution 194.|archive-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711005736/https://bdsmovement.net/bdsintro|dead-url=no}}</ref>

運動組織把以色列和巴勒斯坦的現狀，把以色列對待巴勒斯坦人，在其居住地區興起[[隔離牆|隔離牆]]，與[[南非|南非]]白人統治時對黑人的[[南非种族隔离|種族隔離]]政策[[以色列与南非种族隔离的类比|相提並論]]。

以色列战略事务部称该组织为[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義]]组织<ref>[https://4il.org.il/dowloadFile?ID=mrGE7xwDjRv3QLWVJ81aAoO6n Behind the Mask - The Antisemitic Nature of BDS Exposed]</ref>，並自此積極地向歐美議員遊說[[反BDS法|立法反制]]。

